                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    <locus target="#102v"/>: contains a typical concluding prayer for the <title type="complete" ref="LIT2701Dawit"/>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#ir #iv"/>: pentrials and scrawls
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <desc>
                    It is unclear what manuscript this is in the insurance hand list
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#45v"/>: The midpoint of the <title type="complete" ref="LIT2701Dawit"/> is marked in two ways, with a line of text written entirely in red ink, and with a small harag in the right margin
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#109v"/>: has spaces where text was to have been written in red ink, but was apparently overlooked
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <desc>
                    Psalm 118 contains the spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e6">
                    <desc>
                    Scribal intervention:
                    words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#7v #8r #11v #14r #14v"/>, etc.);
                    and lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#11r #15v #30r #38r #47r"/>, etc.);
                    and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#15v"/>, line 24; <locus target="#16r"/>, line 6; <locus target="#18r"/>, line 22; <locus target="#20r"/>, lines 7 and <locus target="#24"/>; <locus target="#25r"/>, line 16; <locus target="#26v"/>, line 19; etc.);
                    erasure markings are visible (<locus target="#15v"/>); text has been removed (<locus target="#14r #15v #19v #21v #22v"/>, etc.)
                    </desc>
                    </item>

                  </list>
                  </additions>
